State Regulations

Each company shall provide each of its testing stations
required herein by section
229.50
(a)-(d)
of
this Part with appropriate equipment for the determination of the partial
chemical composition (percentages of carbon dioxide, illuminants, oxygen and
carbon monoxide) of gas. Notes
